📢 Work Study Opportunity Applications are Now Open!

Explore paid, on-campus positions at UofT that align with your academic and personal goals. Choose between two streams:
 
💻Research Experience Stream
Faculty-led research
Hands-on experience in your research area
Build your own network

💼Work Experience Stream
Gain valuable work experience
Familiarize yourself with the UofT campus Perfect for developing your résumé

🗓️Applications open on CLNX from August 16 to September 25 (LINK IN BIO)!

Eligibility: Must be an undergrad with at least 2.0 FCE (min 0.5 credits in one session and 1.5 credits in the other).

📢Don’t miss out on this fantastic opportunity!
#WorkStudy #StudentJobs #UofT
